@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram - Microwave Oven

[*] --> DisplayTime

state DisplayTime
DisplayTime : do / display current time

state ChoosePowerLevel <<choice>>
ChoosePowerLevel : [Full Power]
ChoosePowerLevel : [Half Power]

state SetCookingTime
SetCookingTime : entry / user chooses power level and sets cooking time
SetCookingTime : do / set cooking time

state CookingProcess
CookingProcess : entry / start cooking process
CookingProcess : do / cook food with chosen settings
CookingProcess : exit / cooking complete or door opened

state DoorOpenDuringOperation <<choice>>
DoorOpenDuringOperation : [Door Open] --> StopImmediately
DoorOpenDuringOperation : [Door Closed] --> CookingProcess

state StopImmediately
StopImmediately : do / stop immediately when door is opened during cooking process
StopImmediate : exit / return to DisplayTime state

state CancelCookingProcess
CancelCookingProcess : entry / user cancels the cooking process
CancelCookingProcess : do / cancel the cooking process
CancelCookingProcess : exit / return to DisplayTime state

@enduml
